description: This skill gives you a random exercise to do, similar to the "deck of cards" workout program.  Some of the exercises included are push-ups, crunches, and air squats.
exampleInteractions: Alexa, ask Workout Buddy for a workout
Alexa, ask Workout Buddy for an exercise
Alexa, ask Workout Buddy for another one
name: Workout Buddy
shortDescription: This skill gives you a random exercise to do.
